<section id="report" class="page-header">
    <h1>How to Report Problems</h1>
    <p>Your voice can spark real change in your community.</p>
</section>

<section class="report-grid">
    <div class="report-step">
        <h2>Step 1: Document</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Take clear photos</li>
            <li>Record the exact location</li>
            <li>Describe the type of damage</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="report-step">
        <h2>Step 2: Contact the Right Office</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Roads & Bridges:</strong> DPWH or Engineering Office</li>
            <li><strong>Water Systems:</strong> Barangay or Water District</li>
            <li><strong>Schools:</strong> DepEd Division Office</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="report-step">
        <h2>Step 3: Use Official Channels</h2>
        <p><a href="https://feedback.dpwh.gov.ph">DPWH Feedback Portal</a></p>
        <p>8888 Hotline (free on Globe / Smart)</p>
    </div>
</section>

